WEBVTT

01:42.940 --> 01:46.020
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:48.920
[Episode 2]

01:49.100 --> 01:53.410
[Rehabilitation Department]

01:59.650 --> 02:00.530
Are you looking for me?

02:08.820 --> 02:12.030
[POLICE]

02:12.160 --> 02:14.380
[Rehabilitation Department]

02:15.960 --> 02:17.310
♫As the city flickers♫

02:18.650 --> 02:21.500
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

02:22.720 --> 02:24.010
♫And you, who love to smile♫

02:25.030 --> 02:27.480
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

02:28.510 --> 02:30.860
♫The humor of time♫

02:32.230 --> 02:34.790
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

02:35.860 --> 02:41.620
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

02:43.000 --> 02:44.620
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

02:45.730 --> 02:48.590
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

02:49.880 --> 02:51.310
♫The stubborn me♫

02:52.540 --> 02:55.230
♫I always think of the far future♫

02:56.020 --> 02:58.090
♫I walk willfully♫

02:57.600 --> 02:59.950
[POLICE]

02:59.470 --> 03:02.380
♫Like a star revolving around♫

03:03.030 --> 03:04.340
♫I turn around♫

03:05.500 --> 03:09.000
♫But you're not behind me♫

03:10.670 --> 03:12.250
♫Losing you♫

03:13.070 --> 03:15.250
♫It's so unreal♫

03:13.590 --> 03:14.350
Senior.

03:16.440 --> 03:17.870
♫I hurt my love♫

03:18.590 --> 03:19.530
♫But still hope to♫

03:20.280 --> 03:22.970
♫Start anew♫

03:20.690 --> 03:21.760
Why are you here?

03:21.790 --> 03:22.940
I was nearby working on a case.

03:22.970 --> 03:24.300
I rushed here as soon as I got the notice.

03:24.090 --> 03:26.230
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

03:24.430 --> 03:25.120
Are you okay?

03:25.270 --> 03:25.860
I'm fine.

03:25.890 --> 03:27.040
This is Liu Hao from our battalion.

03:27.130 --> 03:29.260
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

03:27.440 --> 03:28.040
Hello.

03:28.130 --> 03:28.950
Director Xing is on his way here.

03:28.990 --> 03:29.910
He said he wants to see you.

03:30.300 --> 03:31.010
Alright, I see.

03:30.660 --> 03:33.050
♫When you're not here♫

03:31.130 --> 03:31.829
You go ahead and get back to work.

03:31.850 --> 03:32.740
I'll get back to it.

03:33.590 --> 03:35.940
♫Life becomes aimless♫

03:36.500 --> 03:39.310
♫I miss you missing me♫

03:47.680 --> 03:50.930
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

03:49.660 --> 03:50.880
Being fearless in the face of danger

03:50.910 --> 03:52.040
and charging towards it.

03:52.290 --> 03:53.200
Jiang,

03:53.590 --> 03:54.510
your son

03:54.550 --> 03:55.510
is really impressive.

03:55.900 --> 03:57.320
He's the pride of our criminal police.

03:58.480 --> 04:00.270
Isn't this just what we should do

04:00.290 --> 04:01.770
as police officers?

04:02.040 --> 04:03.910
This kid still has a long way to go.

04:05.800 --> 04:06.870
This time,

04:07.190 --> 04:08.700
thanks to the medical staff at the hospital,

04:08.860 --> 04:10.080
we were able to successfully

04:10.100 --> 04:10.980
resolve this crisis.

04:11.790 --> 04:12.760
Xing,

04:13.370 --> 04:14.530
you worked hard too.

04:14.550 --> 04:16.120
You were still at the front line.

04:16.600 --> 04:17.339
Alright.

04:17.630 --> 04:18.500
I'm leaving now.

04:19.589 --> 04:20.240
Jiang.

04:20.269 --> 04:20.779
Yes.

04:20.829 --> 04:21.750
Take good care of your dad.

04:22.010 --> 04:22.550
Yes.

04:23.350 --> 04:23.960
Well,

04:23.980 --> 04:25.120
I won't see you off.

04:25.350 --> 04:26.220
Take care.

04:26.900 --> 04:27.670
Director Xing, let me see you off.

04:27.950 --> 04:28.450
Bye.

04:28.480 --> 04:29.000
Goodbye, Uncle.

04:29.020 --> 04:29.980
Get well soon.

04:34.590 --> 04:35.159
Jiang,

04:35.190 --> 04:35.790
please stay.

04:36.159 --> 04:36.800
I'm leaving.

04:36.830 --> 04:37.560
Take care.

04:38.040 --> 04:39.030
Senior, I'm leaving.

04:39.070 --> 04:39.720
Alright. You give Director Xing a ride.

04:39.750 --> 04:40.190
Bye.

04:47.120 --> 04:47.630
Dad,

04:47.960 --> 04:49.060
I've seen Director Xing off.

04:49.770 --> 04:50.170
Sit.

04:54.880 --> 04:55.580
Son,

04:57.380 --> 04:58.659
good job today.

04:59.159 --> 05:00.380
I inherited it from you.

05:04.550 --> 05:05.700
Let me tell you,

05:06.930 --> 05:07.740
I've made up my mind.

05:09.970 --> 05:11.370
I'm going to have the surgery.

05:13.990 --> 05:15.230
This surgery...

05:15.470 --> 05:17.470
The issue is the sick sinus syndrome you have.

05:18.450 --> 05:19.950
The risk of this surgery

05:20.500 --> 05:21.800
is actually quite high.

05:23.630 --> 05:25.360
What doesn't have risks?

05:26.490 --> 05:28.170
Just like when you were defusing the bomb today,

05:28.390 --> 05:29.670
you knew there was a risk,

05:29.830 --> 05:30.880
but you still went for it, right?

05:31.610 --> 05:33.300
Dr. Han told me that

05:33.550 --> 05:34.620
even if

05:34.830 --> 05:36.310
I use conservative treatment

05:36.350 --> 05:37.210
to suppress it this time,

05:37.350 --> 05:38.500
it will relapse in the future.

05:39.140 --> 05:40.800
To cure it completely,

05:40.920 --> 05:42.659
I must undergo this surgery.

05:44.040 --> 05:44.990
Besides,

05:46.320 --> 05:47.830
surgeries are very advanced now.

05:47.980 --> 05:49.090
There's nothing to be afraid of.

05:49.360 --> 05:50.560
As long as you've thought it through.

05:51.430 --> 05:52.190
I have.

05:52.880 --> 05:54.090
I'll consider it defusing a bomb.

05:57.810 --> 05:58.470
Alright.

05:59.150 --> 06:00.070
Go back and rest.

06:00.310 --> 06:01.200
You've had a long day.

06:02.240 --> 06:02.900
Okay.

06:05.090 --> 06:06.220
Rest early.

06:15.670 --> 06:19.690
[Ward 3]

06:26.790 --> 06:27.470
Dr. Han,

06:27.910 --> 06:28.580
hello.

06:29.150 --> 06:30.090
I'm Jiang Chengyi.

06:30.560 --> 06:32.430
Are you available tomorrow morning?

06:32.950 --> 06:34.350
I would still like to

06:34.350 --> 06:35.710
discuss my father's surgical plan with you.

06:37.100 --> 06:39.270
[Compassionate Heart, Skillful Hands, and Patient-centered Care]

06:43.580 --> 06:46.570
[Anesthesia and Postoperative Analgesia Informed Consent Form]

07:04.560 --> 07:06.030
Your husband fell from a high place

07:06.110 --> 07:07.270
while performing his duties

07:07.540 --> 07:09.580
and is currently in the hospital undergoing emergency treatment.

07:24.870 --> 07:26.430
Mom, are you okay?

07:26.840 --> 07:27.690
I'm fine.

07:28.900 --> 07:30.720
I just got smoke in my eyes from the pot.

07:30.750 --> 07:31.470
It's okay.

07:32.190 --> 07:33.590
Has Dad not come back yet?

07:34.100 --> 07:35.320
Isn't he always like this?

07:36.190 --> 07:36.990
But...

07:37.070 --> 07:38.630
it's already very late.

07:40.090 --> 07:40.870
It's okay.

07:42.600 --> 07:44.120
I'm making something delicious for your dad.

07:44.800 --> 07:45.930
Go to bed now.

07:45.960 --> 07:46.909
You have school tomorrow.

07:48.950 --> 07:49.500
Go.

07:49.870 --> 07:50.640
Don't worry.

08:03.920 --> 08:07.360
[Ward 3]

08:07.450 --> 08:08.620
[I still want to discuss my father's surgery plan with you]

08:07.450 --> 08:08.620
[Hello, Dr. Han, this is Jiang Chengyi. May I ask if you are available tomorrow morning?]

08:45.950 --> 08:46.590
Hello.

08:47.740 --> 08:48.190
Lu Yan.

08:48.310 --> 08:48.790
Lu Yan.

08:49.070 --> 08:49.910
I heard you

08:49.910 --> 08:50.620
met Jiang Chengyi.

08:51.290 --> 08:52.720
What happened?

08:52.790 --> 08:53.630
Hurry up and tell me the whole story.

08:53.660 --> 08:54.230
Tell me the details.

08:54.260 --> 08:55.120
What did you two say?

08:57.620 --> 08:58.690
Listen to my command.

08:59.690 --> 09:00.460
I'll count to three,

09:01.930 --> 09:03.050
and you cut this one.

09:03.240 --> 09:04.310
Ready?

09:12.550 --> 09:13.320
Lu Yan,

09:14.050 --> 09:15.170
can you hear me? Hello?

09:16.690 --> 09:17.470
I'll talk to you later.

09:17.470 --> 09:18.340
I'm running.

09:18.510 --> 09:20.030
Don't rush to hang up.

09:20.190 --> 09:21.530
How is Jiang Chengyi doing now?

09:21.560 --> 09:22.880
Does he have a girlfriend?

09:23.190 --> 09:24.110
I don't know.

09:24.240 --> 09:25.020
Let's talk later.

09:25.300 --> 09:27.250
Don't forget to come and be the bridesmaid.

09:30.950 --> 09:31.990
Why is she upset?

09:36.540 --> 09:37.890
Everyone, follow the camera.

09:37.910 --> 09:39.510
Let's see what day it is today.

09:39.510 --> 09:40.440
Such a grand display.

09:40.830 --> 09:42.320
Who's making jokes there?

09:42.550 --> 09:43.660
Isn't this Qin Yong?

09:43.660 --> 09:44.290
Am I handsome?

09:44.430 --> 09:45.030
Long time no see.

09:45.070 --> 09:45.620
You are so handsome.

09:45.710 --> 09:46.600
Happy wedding day!

09:46.710 --> 09:48.000
Drink more.

09:48.270 --> 09:49.050
Hello.

09:49.190 --> 09:49.670
Hello.

09:49.670 --> 09:50.820
Say hello.

09:51.260 --> 09:52.580
Who's taking a photo here?

09:52.750 --> 09:54.270
Let me take a photo of the stars of today's wedding.

09:54.290 --> 09:54.790
The stars.

09:54.910 --> 09:55.790
Look who they are.

09:56.080 --> 09:56.760
That's right.

09:56.790 --> 09:57.820
Zhong Wenxuan

09:57.950 --> 10:00.240
and Tang Jie are getting married!

10:00.830 --> 10:02.300
Hello. Hello.

10:02.600 --> 10:03.150
Where is the bride?

10:03.150 --> 10:03.590
The bride? The bride

10:03.590 --> 10:04.510
is over there.

10:04.610 --> 10:05.710
What a grand display.

10:05.830 --> 10:06.680
There's even a band.

10:09.480 --> 10:11.210
Where's the groom, the man of today?

10:11.550 --> 10:12.370
Zhong Wenxuan?

10:12.910 --> 10:13.780
Zhong?

10:14.630 --> 10:16.500
I fell in love with you at first sight

10:16.590 --> 10:18.390
the first time we met in college.

10:18.470 --> 10:19.120
Let's take a look.

10:19.200 --> 10:20.430
Look at our main character.

10:20.510 --> 10:21.810
Who is our main character?

10:22.000 --> 10:22.630
Zhong Wenxuan!

10:22.650 --> 10:23.950
How's the preparation going?

10:25.040 --> 10:25.890
It's almost ready.

10:26.510 --> 10:27.270
Let me give it a try.

10:27.270 --> 10:27.870
Okay. Come on.

10:31.980 --> 10:32.920
Tang Jue...

10:34.260 --> 10:35.250
Awesome, brother.

10:35.370 --> 10:36.450
You said the wrong name.

10:38.060 --> 10:38.810
I'm too nervous.

10:39.090 --> 10:39.560
Don't be nervous.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.070
One more time.

10:40.090 --> 10:40.460
Okay.

10:41.690 --> 10:42.460
Tang Jie,

10:43.270 --> 10:44.490
I fell in love with you

10:45.580 --> 10:46.890
at first sight

10:47.670 --> 10:48.590
the first time

10:49.360 --> 10:50.360
we met in college.

10:51.740 --> 10:54.540
Our lives are only 30 years long.

10:56.630 --> 10:57.110
Bro,

10:57.110 --> 10:58.580
the wedding is about to start.

10:58.610 --> 10:59.710
Can you remember it?

11:00.400 --> 11:01.380
Don't interrupt me while I'm memorizing my speech.

11:01.570 --> 11:02.590
Don't be nervous.

11:02.700 --> 11:03.400
Alright, alright.

11:04.060 --> 11:05.280
I tried on many dresses that day,

11:05.300 --> 11:06.410
and this one looked the best.

11:07.460 --> 11:08.390
Tang Jie,

11:08.550 --> 11:10.490
your wedding photos are so beautiful.

11:11.710 --> 11:12.350
Really?

11:12.430 --> 11:13.030
Come on.

11:13.050 --> 11:13.790
Let's take a photo.

11:13.810 --> 11:14.680
-Come on.
-Let's do it together.

11:18.360 --> 11:19.230
I'll send you the photo

11:19.230 --> 11:19.510
once I've finished editing.

11:19.510 --> 11:20.040
Okay.

11:20.090 --> 11:23.720
[Tang Jie and Zhong Wenxuan]

11:20.290 --> 11:21.190
Jie,

11:21.230 --> 11:22.390
your wedding dress is so beautiful.

11:22.450 --> 11:23.790
It really flatters your figure.

11:23.840 --> 11:25.150
Is it custom-made?

11:25.590 --> 11:26.230
Yes.

11:27.460 --> 11:28.180
I said

11:28.230 --> 11:28.830
just rent one,

11:28.850 --> 11:29.960
but Zhong refused.

11:30.160 --> 11:31.380
Isn't a wedding dress something

11:31.410 --> 11:31.970
you only wear once

11:31.990 --> 11:33.430
and then leave in the wardrobe collecting dust?

11:33.700 --> 11:34.390
It's a good thing for your husband

11:34.390 --> 11:35.430
to spend money on you.

11:35.940 --> 11:36.560
I think

11:36.590 --> 11:37.590
you are just humblebragging.

11:37.750 --> 11:38.660
I'm not.

11:38.890 --> 11:39.680
I said,

11:39.720 --> 11:41.040
"If you have too much money to spend,

11:41.070 --> 11:41.750
make me

11:41.790 --> 11:42.660
a gold lab coat.

11:42.710 --> 11:44.310
I can wear it to work, and it holds its value"

11:44.350 --> 11:45.290
Jie.

11:44.420 --> 11:47.150
[Tang Jie and Zhong Wenxuan]

11:45.710 --> 11:46.400
Look.

11:47.670 --> 11:48.980
These two pictures.

11:49.870 --> 11:51.360
Why is Deng Man in the picture?

11:51.540 --> 11:52.420
Delete it now.

11:52.460 --> 11:53.880
If Yan Yan sees it later, we're doomed.

11:53.900 --> 11:54.810
Delete it.

11:54.950 --> 11:55.640
Delete it now.

11:55.660 --> 11:56.710
After that, make sure

11:56.750 --> 11:57.280
to check for other photos.

11:58.450 --> 11:59.050
Look here.

11:59.140 --> 11:59.770
Come here.

11:59.800 --> 12:00.740
Here.

12:10.260 --> 12:11.450
You all are here?

12:13.690 --> 12:15.820
It's my wedding. Of course they are here.

12:16.170 --> 12:17.200
Congratulations, Jie.

12:18.790 --> 12:20.390
Happy wedding day, Jie.

12:20.620 --> 12:21.400
Thank you,

12:21.650 --> 12:22.330
Ding Jing,

12:22.450 --> 12:23.570
Liu Yujie.

12:25.390 --> 12:26.610
Long time no see.

12:26.900 --> 12:28.560
I haven't finished my makeup.

12:28.590 --> 12:29.500
Why don't you two go out

12:29.530 --> 12:30.380
and find something to eat?

12:30.410 --> 12:31.140
I know.

12:31.260 --> 12:32.390
I came to see you first

12:32.820 --> 12:34.380
and give you the gift I prepared for you.

12:38.400 --> 12:39.660
So valuable?

12:39.680 --> 12:40.410
Thanks.

12:40.440 --> 12:41.120
It's nothing.

12:41.330 --> 12:42.140
Just a small gift.

12:42.680 --> 12:43.820
I wish you and...

12:44.480 --> 12:45.250
that...

12:46.360 --> 12:47.060
Zhong.

12:47.990 --> 12:48.820
Yes, Zhong.

12:48.850 --> 12:50.600
I do remember his name is Zhong.

12:50.620 --> 12:51.620
Yes, Zhong.

12:51.640 --> 12:52.450
I wish you a happy wedding day

12:52.470 --> 12:53.420
and may you grow old together.

12:53.990 --> 12:54.770
Thank you.

12:55.290 --> 12:56.730
Who from our class came?

12:56.750 --> 12:57.960
Did Jiang Chengyi come?

12:59.220 --> 13:00.190
He did, I think.

13:00.190 --> 13:01.000
Maybe he's outside.

13:01.580 --> 13:02.240
Okay.

13:02.760 --> 13:03.400
Continue with your makeup.

13:03.430 --> 13:04.640
I'll go and play with him.

13:08.850 --> 13:09.350
That's

13:09.370 --> 13:10.990
too cheesy.

13:11.030 --> 13:11.950
She never called me Jie

13:11.950 --> 13:12.990
when we were in school.

13:13.010 --> 13:13.820
Exactly.

13:13.840 --> 13:15.110
That was so dramatic.

13:15.150 --> 13:16.550
Who exactly is getting married today?

13:16.670 --> 13:17.820
She has another target.

13:17.910 --> 13:18.600
Obviously,

13:18.630 --> 13:19.750
she's here for Jiang Chengyi.

13:19.880 --> 13:21.370
She was pursuing him back in school.

13:21.400 --> 13:23.240
It's been eight years,

13:23.260 --> 13:24.560
and she still hasn't given up.

13:24.600 --> 13:25.030
Hurry up

13:25.030 --> 13:25.710
and give me my phone.

13:25.710 --> 13:26.790
I'll send a WeChat message to Lu Yan.

13:27.090 --> 13:27.840
Got it.

13:27.870 --> 13:29.070
I'll be right there. I'm on my way.

13:28.970 --> 13:36.970
[Outpatient]

13:57.350 --> 13:59.820
Ding Jing also came to the wedding.

13:59.840 --> 14:01.570
Oh my gosh, what's going on here?

14:01.840 --> 14:03.360
Where are you now?

14:07.700 --> 14:10.160
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

14:13.750 --> 14:14.910
Get in. I'll give you a ride.

14:15.160 --> 14:16.850
No need, I'll just call a cab.

14:17.730 --> 14:19.010
Can you get a cab at this time?

14:21.410 --> 14:22.160
[There are few cars nearby. We're still calling a taxi for you]

14:25.540 --> 14:26.160
Come on.

15:06.630 --> 15:07.680
How is...

15:09.150 --> 15:09.850
that patient?

15:10.590 --> 15:11.620
Can he survive?

15:12.040 --> 15:13.210
He's still in the ICU,

15:13.780 --> 15:14.520
but his vital signs

15:14.550 --> 15:15.510
have returned to normal.

15:15.910 --> 15:16.900
Don't worry.

15:17.360 --> 15:18.340
We'll do our best.

15:20.890 --> 15:22.260
Well...

15:23.160 --> 15:24.430
How did you deal with the person

15:24.430 --> 15:25.430
who made the bomb

15:27.220 --> 15:28.160
in the end?

15:28.720 --> 15:29.580
I don't know.

15:31.090 --> 15:32.540
Are the police

15:32.760 --> 15:33.750
not allowed to disclose details

15:33.760 --> 15:35.280
about things like this?

15:36.560 --> 15:37.350
No.

15:38.370 --> 15:39.930
This isn't part of my job.

15:47.150 --> 15:48.930
[On the call]

15:47.940 --> 15:48.890
Hello, Jiang.

15:49.210 --> 15:50.500
Let me tell you.

15:50.530 --> 15:52.040
I have a surprise for you today.

15:52.230 --> 15:53.070
As my best man,

15:53.070 --> 15:54.100
you'll definitely gain something.

15:54.380 --> 15:56.020
Guess who the bridesmaid is today?

15:56.590 --> 15:57.670
Lu Yan!

15:58.000 --> 15:58.790
Are you happy?

15:59.040 --> 15:59.980
Are you excited?

16:00.030 --> 16:02.110
Haven't you always wanted to see her?

16:03.500 --> 16:04.890
-Well…
-Did you hear me?

16:05.560 --> 16:07.110
Lu Yan is in my car now.

16:09.960 --> 16:10.680
Hello?

16:11.440 --> 16:12.510
The connection is bad.

16:12.540 --> 16:13.320
I'm hanging up now.

16:17.790 --> 16:18.940
These people

16:19.550 --> 16:20.480
are really gossipy.

16:21.540 --> 16:22.470
Yesterday,

16:23.010 --> 16:24.690
Tang Jie also called me

16:24.860 --> 16:25.610
and asked about you.

16:26.920 --> 16:27.670
It's fine.

16:27.710 --> 16:28.980
I won't take it seriously.

16:31.600 --> 16:33.180
But there is one thing that's true.

16:33.920 --> 16:35.380
I do want to see you.

16:43.120 --> 16:44.470
Don't you...

16:46.630 --> 16:48.430
still owe me an explanation?

16:55.070 --> 16:56.760
What exactly happened back then?

17:21.160 --> 17:22.530
You go in first. I'll park the car.

17:50.190 --> 17:50.930
Sixth floor.

17:51.300 --> 17:52.350
The chocolates you arranged

17:52.380 --> 17:52.870
have already

17:52.910 --> 17:53.990
been sent in.

17:54.890 --> 17:55.880
Open one for me first.

18:02.350 --> 18:03.070
Wait for me downstairs.

18:03.090 --> 18:03.670
Okay.

18:08.210 --> 18:09.020
Lu Yan.

18:11.000 --> 18:11.870
Senior Wen?

18:12.150 --> 18:13.340
You've returned from abroad?

18:13.470 --> 18:14.740
I came back a couple of days ago.

18:16.160 --> 18:18.330
Tang Jie mentioned that day

18:18.390 --> 18:20.390
that Zhong was upset

18:20.430 --> 18:21.370
because you couldn't come back.

18:21.460 --> 18:22.360
He said your basketball team

18:22.390 --> 18:23.380
couldn't get all its members together.

18:23.750 --> 18:25.090
Of course, I would come back.

18:25.120 --> 18:26.760
I even sponsored their wedding candy.

18:26.840 --> 18:27.700
Really?

18:27.800 --> 18:28.800
What kind of wedding candy?

18:29.640 --> 18:30.530
I just happened to bring one with me.

18:33.630 --> 18:34.550
Chocolate?

18:36.130 --> 18:38.170
This brand is hard to find.

18:38.440 --> 18:39.710
I bought them when I

18:39.730 --> 18:40.420
was at Fashion Week.

18:41.260 --> 18:42.690
I really love it.

18:43.450 --> 18:44.170
I know.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.280
When you were in college,

18:46.310 --> 18:47.870
you used to carry a lot of candy and chocolate

18:47.870 --> 18:48.610
in your pockets.

18:48.910 --> 18:50.310
Yeah. You still remember that?

18:50.550 --> 18:51.700
When we were in college,

18:51.830 --> 18:52.560
your basketball team

18:52.590 --> 18:53.790
played so hard

18:53.870 --> 18:54.710
that it was easy to get low blood sugar.

18:54.770 --> 18:56.270
So, I carried candy with me every day.

18:56.350 --> 18:57.470
Jiang Chengyi used to call me

18:57.510 --> 18:59.210
a mobile snack shop.

19:07.520 --> 19:08.470
The elevator is here.

19:08.650 --> 19:09.440
Let's go.

19:23.760 --> 19:24.610
Jiang Chengyi?

19:24.930 --> 19:25.780
What a coincidence.

19:28.510 --> 19:29.130
Yes.

19:49.990 --> 19:50.660
Lu Yan,

19:51.330 --> 19:52.390
how's Mr. Han's

19:52.410 --> 19:53.090
health?

19:53.590 --> 19:55.390
Dr. Han? He's doing well.

19:55.410 --> 19:56.170
He just

19:56.340 --> 19:57.690
really misses you.

19:58.070 --> 19:59.630
He told his students in class,

19:59.650 --> 20:00.690
"None of you write papers

20:00.920 --> 20:02.920
as well as a student of mine."

20:03.900 --> 20:05.180
Does he still eat pancake rolls

20:05.290 --> 20:06.670
with fried dough sticks for breakfast?

20:06.960 --> 20:07.620
Yes.

20:08.100 --> 20:09.930
His cholesterol is high, so he doesn't dare to eat them.

20:10.070 --> 20:10.640
So,

20:10.730 --> 20:12.200
he secretly eats them behind his wife's back.

20:14.080 --> 20:15.010
Next weekend,

20:15.260 --> 20:17.470
if you don't have surgery scheduled,

20:17.550 --> 20:18.210
I'll host

20:18.360 --> 20:19.420
a meal

20:19.470 --> 20:20.050
for Dr. Han,

20:20.060 --> 20:20.690
his wife,

20:21.230 --> 20:23.230
you,

20:23.250 --> 20:24.520
and the juniors.

20:24.760 --> 20:26.430
If it's okay with you,

20:26.450 --> 20:27.600
you can show me

20:38.470 --> 20:39.450
You left your lipstick in my car.

20:42.110 --> 20:42.840
Thank you.

20:45.490 --> 20:46.120
Let's go.

20:53.710 --> 20:54.590
Good. One more time.

20:54.590 --> 20:55.420
Let's try another pose.

20:55.550 --> 20:56.270
Finger hearts.

20:56.310 --> 20:57.070
Try to look a bit more cheerful!

20:57.140 --> 20:57.630
Okay.

20:57.710 --> 20:58.750
One, two, three.

20:58.920 --> 20:59.880
Cheese.

21:00.590 --> 21:01.550
Take care of the guests for me, Ping.

21:01.630 --> 21:02.030
Okay.

21:02.030 --> 21:02.860
Go over there first.

21:02.920 --> 21:04.000
Drink more, Qin Yong.

21:04.270 --> 21:05.190
Zhong.

21:06.880 --> 21:07.500
You're here.

21:07.530 --> 21:08.470
Isn't this Captain Jiang?

21:08.470 --> 21:09.070
Congratulations.

21:09.930 --> 21:10.720
Come here, Yan.

21:10.750 --> 21:11.870
You look so beautiful.

21:12.590 --> 21:13.930
Why did you two come together?

21:15.630 --> 21:16.900
We met on the way.

21:18.350 --> 21:19.530
Why are you two here together?

21:20.100 --> 21:21.410
We met on the way.

21:21.750 --> 21:23.060
I mean you and Wen Peng.

21:25.050 --> 21:26.450
We met on the way.

21:27.620 --> 21:28.520
What a coincidence.

21:28.920 --> 21:29.470
What a coincidence.

21:29.470 --> 21:29.910
What a coincidence.

21:31.160 --> 21:31.740
Tang Jie,

21:31.900 --> 21:32.620
Da Zhong.

21:32.810 --> 21:33.990
May you grow old together.

21:34.830 --> 21:35.770
Senior.

21:35.800 --> 21:37.120
Thank you for the wedding candy.

21:37.190 --> 21:37.710
It really elevated

21:37.750 --> 21:38.880
the level of our wedding.

21:39.030 --> 21:39.510
You're welcome.

21:39.710 --> 21:40.550
Just a small gesture.

21:41.040 --> 21:41.810
What a sweet talker.

21:42.830 --> 21:43.390
Let's take a photo.

21:43.430 --> 21:43.790
Let's take a photo.

21:43.820 --> 21:44.710
Come on.

21:44.750 --> 21:45.230
Let's take a photo.

21:52.740 --> 21:54.800
The bride should be in the middle, right?

21:55.740 --> 21:57.350
Then I'll go to that side.

22:04.470 --> 22:05.440
We still need one person here.

22:05.990 --> 22:07.110
How about having one more person over here?

22:07.150 --> 22:07.900
Jiang.

22:10.250 --> 22:10.890
I'll go.

22:16.870 --> 22:17.580
Come on.

22:29.040 --> 22:31.690
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

22:32.460 --> 22:35.480
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

22:36.640 --> 22:39.020
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

22:39.640 --> 22:42.600
