24:21.270 --> 24:21.980
I...

24:22.200 --> 24:22.810
I...

24:23.440 --> 24:24.120
I...

24:24.650 --> 24:25.600
What's wrong?

24:25.620 --> 24:26.520
Just say it.

24:26.840 --> 24:27.700
I...

24:28.610 --> 24:29.690
Give your speech.

24:34.390 --> 24:36.430
From the first moment I saw you,

24:38.030 --> 24:40.290
From the first moment I saw you,

24:43.810 --> 24:45.290
I fell in love with you.

24:46.720 --> 24:48.360
I fell in love with you.

24:53.120 --> 24:54.360
Although our lives

24:54.390 --> 24:55.470
haven't yet reached 30 years,

24:57.270 --> 24:58.630
Although our lives

24:58.650 --> 24:59.860
haven't yet reached 30 years,

25:02.720 --> 25:04.210
I've already spent

25:05.020 --> 25:06.770
more than a third of that time loving you.

25:07.630 --> 25:09.320
I've already spent

25:09.640 --> 25:11.460
more than a third of that time loving you.

25:12.690 --> 25:13.900
For the rest of my life,

25:15.420 --> 25:17.060
I will never miss a single second with you.

25:18.630 --> 25:19.830
For the rest of my life,

25:20.440 --> 25:22.620
I will never miss a single second with you.

25:35.800 --> 25:39.770
[Happiness Station]

25:40.870 --> 25:41.920
[Happiness Station]

25:48.740 --> 25:49.620
Jiang Chengyi,

25:50.710 --> 25:51.550
what's wrong?

25:59.600 --> 26:00.620
Let's get married.

26:07.160 --> 26:07.770
